{"tid":660932,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"物理神人請賜教","createTime":"2018-05-11T06:12:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-11T06:12:26.000Z","uid":9506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e98b6c8cd994fedf673f9babc174a86fae8f2bfb","tid":660932,"uid":9506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T06:12:26.000Z","msg":"假設宜家有一個coupled mass spring system，係由六七個not identical既mass同幾條not identical既spring組成，好似層層疊咁樣垂直排好，類似係咁。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/11/140935_5a07e4e5daf5dd0186c97f8f74634aa2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F11%2F140935_5a07e4e5daf5dd0186c97f8f74634aa2.png&h=e0672cc9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當有external vibration(上下震動)從整個system的底部向上傳送的時侯，試解釋為何：<br />\n(1) 所有mass既vibrational frequency都會一樣<br />\n(2) 每個mass既phase angle並不一樣<br />\n(3) 每個mass既vibrational amplitude並不一樣"}]}